other_tests.findings: Presence of in vitro inducible macrolide–lincosamide–streptogramin B resistance (iMLS) in pretreatment isolate.
other_tests.changes_over_time: In vitro iMLS confirmed in postclindamycin operative isolate.

other_tests.findings: Moderate number of polymorphonuclear leukocytes and a few gram-positive cocci.
MRSA grew on a culture of the debrided material.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Isolates had a susceptibility profile similar to previous isolates, except postclindamycin which revealed resistance to clindamycin.

other_tests.findings: Both preclindamycin and postclindamycin isolates were genetically identical.
